[Kier] <i>Mark S..</i>

330
00:37:30.959 --> 00:37:35.839
<i>in completing your 25th Macrodata file.</i>

331
00:37:36.965 --> 00:37:42.846
<i>you have drawn my grand agendum
nearer to fulfillment.</i>

332
00:37:43.388 --> 00:37:46.057
