important people in history.</i>

334
00:37:52.481 --> 00:37:56.485
<i>Revel now in the fruit of your labors.</i>

335
00:37:57.110 --> 00:38:01.364
<i>and hail your earthbound steward.</i>

336
00:38:01.365 --> 00:38:03.575
